must.be.logged: You must be logged in before FizzBuzz!
passw.no.match.confirm: Confirmation and password do not match
helpcomment: This one uses data in memory, that is to say, every time you open the app or refresh the browser the stored data will be lost. :(
helpcomment1: Log in or register in the user menu (right upper corner). Once you are logged in, click the user menu again, you can switch the language. If you change the language it will be stored within the current user.
helpcomment2: By default there is a predefined user, username "user" and password "12345". Enjoy!
